name: Add-on Popularity
query:
SELECT
    `tabAirplane Ticket Add-on Item`.`add_on_type` AS `Add-On Type`,
    COUNT(*) AS `Sold Count`
FROM
    `tabAirplane Ticket Add-on Item`
JOIN
    `tabAirplane Ticket` ON `tabAirplane Ticket Add-on Item`.`parent` = `tabAirplane Ticket`.`name`
GROUP BY
    `tabAirplane Ticket Add-on Item`.`add_on_type`
ORDER BY
    `Sold Count` DESC;
